\nBgm 故事 人物 配音<br />\nFf tales of 系列 蒼藍 呢d有好幾集會玩到喊<br />\n爆完睇完結局都仲會回味多幾日<br />\n<br />\n講系統畫面歐美個堆係贏嘅<br />\n但比唔到個種感覺我"},{"pid":"f3403f2c8424c55432762dc040cc080bcb801b85","tid":99086,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:17:09.000Z","msg":"日系<br />\n歐美個格調始終唔係好啱口味"},{"pid":"838dd56768995a4ea955e18c432208a82641aebb","tid":99086,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日系定義係日本公司出？<br />\n而家bio,ds,mg之類都係日本公司但又好歐美化wor</blockquote><br />\n指日本風格既，唔係指日本公司出，所以我內文係話日式/動漫風格</blockquote><br />\npso2 係韓系<br />\n<br />\n日系無強化 機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558d6bae4c17525b40d17a4aa0fcc05cdf04bdc8","tid":99086,"uid":77218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:19:58.000Z","msg":"歐系，真人風格好玩好多"},{"pid":"7f22699b9798c76358614cf956785d5103411a32","tid":99086,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:22:05.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n日系動作同射擊等等既game無歐美咁好玩<br />\n但日系rpg係做得幾好，故事編排都比歐美好<br />\n但操控好多都好生硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如要你企定定聽npc鳩up<br />\n好多地圖位都會有玻璃卡住你咁唔比行（絕大部分）"},{"pid":"00739d0e53959c3f941c390cfc597c7703dc5504","tid":99086,"uid":77218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我中意heavy rain, beyond two souls 果種 story based 既game, 有冇同好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同好heavy rain 個故仔好撚正<br />\n最近再玩 until dawn<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6fee8aa79d42a6d00b9a4db10599c228b5cf91","tid":99086,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T00:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句<br />\n日系動作同射擊等等既game無歐美咁好玩<br />\n但日系rpg係做得幾好，故事編排都比歐美好<br />\n但操控好多都好生硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 